news.title: Kochi: Residents looking to rise above flood risk by lifting their houses
news.para: House-lifting firms have been receiving enquiries from residents in Kadavanthra, Kaloor, Pachalam, Elamakkara and other areas in the city.

news.title: On Day 1 of its survey, Chandigarh housing board checks 576 Ram Darbar flats
news.para: The teams were carrying legal documents of flats, owners’ details, days of allotment and pictures of original allottees with them, tallying it with information given by the allottees.

news.title: As SC order draws the line, all eyes now on forest conservation act changes
news.para: The FC Amendment Bill has already been listed for introduction in the current session of Parliament, which aims to clarify the applicability of the Act in various types of land and to streamline the process of approvals under the Act.
